title: MyWamp Server Portable
description:
Description:

MyWamp is a portable web server application for Windows, as well as a complete web development environment. It allows you to easily create applications with Apache, PHP, and MySQL all while being completely portable accross Windows machines.

MyWamp Server also comes pre-packaged with several web applications that provide useful services for database backup and recovery and even a web-based IDE. Many more features coming soon!
